From: sOkam <7308253+heysokam@users.noreply.github.com>
Subject: [PATCH] Change protocol prefix from q3a to defrag

Change protocol prefix from q3a to defrag

Files: code/client/cl_main.c

Co-authored-by: Jelle <jelle.vandeweyer@scarlet.be>
---
diff --git a/code/client/cl_main.c b/code/client/cl_main.c
index 9e23d282..e5a87a6d 100644
--- a/code/client/cl_main.c
+++ b/code/client/cl_main.c
@@ -1575,9 +1575,9 @@ static void CL_Connect_f( void ) {
 	Q_strncpyz( buffer, server, sizeof( buffer ) );
 	server = buffer;
 
-	// skip leading "q3a:/" in connection string
-	if ( !Q_stricmpn( server, "q3a:/", 5 ) ) {
-		server += 5;
+	// skip leading "defrag:/" in connection string
+	if ( !Q_stricmpn( server, "defrag:/", 8 ) ) {
+		server += 8;
 	}
 
 	// skip all slash prefixes

-- 
